In this practical we will be creating Telegram Bot using python and the telepot package.
Step 1:- Go to telegram and search BotFather in telegram and text /start which replies with a messgae to start a new bot.
step 2:- To craete a new bot of your name use /nebot.
Step 3:- You need to give a username for your bot.
Step 4:- Once we get the username, an message with a token number of our username arrives.
Step 5:- Then using import telegram and using token number we can connect with our bot.
Step 6:- We can give updates using /getUpdates.
Step 7:- Then after using token number and chat id we can chat with our bot.
